    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPERIENCE CONFINEMENT</h2>When your daily life is confined to a small area, you start to take a closer look at the familiar. See how the crisis impacts your usual environment.<br><br>CHESTNUT GROVE is a short first-person experience, created to document the early days of the COVID-19 pandemic through a personal lens.<br><br>This game is a <strong>short walking simulator with some light puzzles</strong> and can usually be completed within 30 minutes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248590/extras/32cad58a2c61fb143b7e362cbb8d5eeb.poster.avif?t=1674489438\" width=550 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248590/extras/32cad58a2c61fb143b7e362cbb8d5eeb.webm?t=1674489438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248590/extras/32cad58a2c61fb143b7e362cbb8d5eeb.mp4?t=1674489438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>a short first-person experience portraying life during the early COVID-19 pandemic.<br></li><li>a focus on atmosphere and mood.<br></li><li>all documents featured within the game are authentic and taken from real life<br></li><li>light puzzles and environmental interactions.</li></ul>",
